            title="Optional">
        <span id="appid_csharp">

        <span id="objectid_csharp">

</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">string</span>

            title="Optional">
        <span id="principalid_csharp">

        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">string</span>

            title="Optional">
        <span id="principalname_csharp">
